      "text": "In the course of doing research for this project, it was discovered that the security agencies did not quite remain impartial and balanced in their roles because of the alleged well-known incidence of corruption especially by the police. It was stated that when farmers reported cases of Fulani /Bororo herdsmen’s destruction of farms, the police often demanded gratification from complainants before taking action. "
